OL,5, How much did the people running the    
OL,6, Post Office get paid while the flawed  
OL,7, Horizon system was in place?           
OL,9,FBy looking through the company accounts
OL,10,Ffor the Post Office and Royal Mail, the
OL,11,FBBC has come up with a figure - #19.4m 
OL,12,Fover 24 years.                         
OL,14,FBefore 2012, Royal Mail and the Post   
OL,15,FOffice were part of the same           
OL,16,Forganisation - and its three successive
OL,17,Fchief executives, John Roberts, Adam   
OL,18,FCrozier and Dame Moya Greene, made a   
OL,19,Ftotal of #12.8m. All three of them are 
OL,20,Fdue to appear at Horizon Inquiry which 
OL,21,Fresumes on 9 April.                    
